'''Carnography''' is writing, films, images, or other material that contains gratuitous amounts of [[blood]]shed, [[violence]] and/or [[weaponry]]. It is named by analogy to [[pornography]] (although it is often mistaken for a [[portmanteau]] of "carnage" and "pornography", this is not strictly the case), and is sometimes referred to as "violence porn".

The mere depiction of violent acts, or of their results, does not necessarily qualify a film as carnography, just as the mere depiction of sex acts does not necessarily qualify a film as pornography.

